<p>Dear <%= email %></p>
<p>A <%= @tn_role == "broker" ? "Broker" : "Seller" %> has initiated an escrow transaction on TradeNAIRA with you. The time and date is
	<%= @escrow.created_at %>.</p>
<p>The Seller’s email address is <%= @escrow.seller_email  %></p>	

<p>Your role is as a Buyer and the <%= @tn_role == "broker" ? "Broker" : "Seller" %> has specified that the <%= @escrow.fee_payer %> will pay the fees for this transaction.</p>

<p>Please find details of the transaction below. Let us know immediately if any changes need to be made.</p>	

<p>Type of transaction: <%= @escrow.tn_type %></p>
<p>Transaction amount: <%= @escrow.tn_amount %><%= @escrow.tn_currency.upcase %> </p>
<p>What are you buying: <%= @escrow.item_name %></p>
<p>Seller’s email: <%= @escrow.seller_email  %></p>
<%= if @escrow.seller_phone  %>
	<p>Buyer’s phone number: <%= @escrow.seller_phone  %></p>
<% end %>
<% if @escrow.shipping_amount  %>
	<p>Shipping costs: <%= @escrow.shipping_amount  %><%= @escrow.shipping_currency  %></p>
<% else %>	
	<p>Shipping costs: none</p>
<% end %>	
<p>Length of inspection period: <%= @escrow.inspection_length  %></p>

<p>Descriptions and important notes: 
	<%= @escrow.descriptions.nil? ? "none" : @escrow.descriptions  %>
</p>
<p>Please sign up to TradeNAIRA to accept the terms and conditions. We may be in touch to verify details of this transaction with you.</p>

<p>As you are the Buyer, once you have accepted the terms these funds will be blocked in your account to carry out this transaction.</p>

<p>Best Regards</p>
